    FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE AND NONINFRINGEMENT. IN NO EVENT SHALL THE
    AUTHORS OR COPYRIGHT HOLDERS BE LIABLE FOR ANY CLAIM, DAMAGES OR OTHER
    LIABILITY, WHETHER IN AN ACTION OF CONTRACT, TORT OR OTHERWISE, ARISING FROM,
    OUT OF OR IN CONNECTION WITH THE SOFTWARE OR THE USE OR OTHER DEALINGS IN THE
    SOFTWARE.


2. Logo assets
--------------

The logo image files under `logos/` are the property of their respective
owners. They are trademarks and/or copyrighted works of the governing bodies,
class associations, sponsors, and clubs they identify. They are NOT licensed to
you by this repository.

They are hosted here in good faith, to be used by scorers and event organisers
who have a legitimate connection to the entity in question — a sponsorship
agreement, membership of or representation of the club, or the running of that
class's event — for the ordinary purpose of identifying that entity on sailing
results and related materials. The marks are reproduced unaltered (format and
size normalisation only) and displayed in the associative context their owners
intend.

If you are the owner of a logo hosted here and want it removed or corrected,
email mark@hyc.ie. Removal requests are actioned promptly. See README.md
("Takedown").

Per-asset provenance — where each file was obtained, when, and any usage terms
the owner published — is recorded in data/manifest.json.
